{"tid":1616132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[眠建聯] 禁蒙面法推動組記者會 新晉矇眼KOL 劉毅","createTime":"2019-10-03T09:55:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T02:18:31.000Z","uid":57535,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"3a7236ca9072689f7d77972b92690d05bbc57d5a","tid":1616132,"uid":57535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T09:55:40.000Z","msg":"相信大家今日睇蒙面法都覺得on99 成個記者會不值一題<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n惟一最真心既位係葛珮帆講野個陣 佢黨友就算錢已袋都屌唔住 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">誓死都要瞓</span></strong></span>!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>精彩重溫</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/isyeuY7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FisyeuY7.jpg&h=a9f2b671&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GGAc05N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGGAc05N.jpg&h=e386a2c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n農夫有云<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">香港人係鐵人 係最勤奮既市民<br />\n佢唔知我地每人都有同一個精神<br />\n就係無乜精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢位貼地眠建聯新晉梯隊 等我介紹下大家識先</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tau5BD7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTau5BD7.jpg&h=cb913dcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>先簡介下佢背景</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/article/318330\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F318330&d=Sqlr%2BNOTUp1GXDSzM%2FaCEhphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=e29ad402\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/article/318330</a><br />\n民建聯南區社區幹事劉毅 真劍橋碩士<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又狂讀書 又狂做野 唔怪得唔夠訓到打左10次飛機咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n亦證明學歷同人既智力/良心冇直接關係<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">人一藍 腦便殘</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人一紅 眼都矇</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/article/318330\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F318330&d=Sqlr%2BNOTUp1GXDSzM%2FaCEhphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=e29ad402\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/article/318330</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>詳細資料</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">姓名：劉毅 Lau Ngai Victor<br />\n職業 / 身份：律師 (註冊資料: <a href=\"http://www.hklawsoc.org.hk/pub_e/memberlawlist/member.asp?id=987070\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hklawsoc.org.hk%2Fpub_e%2Fmemberlawlist%2Fmember.asp%3Fid%3D987070&d=Sqlr%2BNOTUp1GXDSzM%2FaCEhphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=7e04430c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hklawsoc.org.hk/pub_e/memberlawlist/member.asp?id=987070</a>)<br />\n電話號碼：93864595 / 25552476<br />\n地址：錦繡花園 (Office: 香港中環德己立街2-18號業豐大廈9字樓905A-B室)<br />\nEmail: victor@vlau.hk / victorlau232000@gmail.com<br />\n年齡 / 生日日期：27 / 23AUG1992<br />\n父母：劉豹 (2003年已一賤成名 <a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20030728/3437109\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20030728%2F3437109&d=Sqlr%2BNOTUp1GXDSzM%2FaCEhphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=d4ba5445\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20030728%2F3437109&h=b4b1d6ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20030728/3437109</a>)<br />\n學校：DBS, HKU(Blaw), Cambridge(Criminology, Huges Hall)<br />\nFacebook：Victor Lau(劉毅) - 已關<br />\nInstagram：vic_n_lau</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>進共經驗</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uJBvNMm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuJBvNMm.jpg&h=922f498b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dATeuZH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdATeuZH.jpg&h=b34efba1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rQDqBEH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrQDqBEH.jpg&h=725864f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UC4JojJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUC4JojJ.jpg&h=84652abf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2P6jF6o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2P6jF6o.jpg&h=98a72240&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LOCKSc4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLOCKSc4.jpg&h=20d1b09c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RrYFqx4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRrYFqx4.jpg&h=852b13fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8syeuZL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8syeuZL.jpg&h=db412d99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xS2ferq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxS2ferq.jpg&h=f1da039d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C4e5BEM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC4e5BEM.jpg&h=fab85be4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">古有劉江華 今有張華峰 後有劉毅<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\"><del>不過會唔會